<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em>“叶落归根，人的归属，也许从一生的开始就已经注定。轻叹一声，我不再留恋，转身向汽车走去。”</em></p>
<p>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nicolasl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3517712); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3517712&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607574951" alt="NicolasL" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3517712)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nicolasl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3517712); return false;">NicolasL</a></span></p>
