<div style="display: inline-block; border-radius: 10px; border:dashed 1px #444444; background:#F5F5F5; float:top; width:96.5%; padding:10px">
<p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/vehicle-rampant-tide">载具狂潮</a></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em>“载具已经占领了这个世界，汽车流水线大幅度下降，导致经济大萧条时代再次到来……车祸频频发生……爆炸随时随地都会来临……航船触礁也是……飞机坠毁都是如此……”</em></p>
<p>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bacon-coinber" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4861423); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4861423&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607574951" alt="Bacon Coinber" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4861423)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bacon-coinber" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4861423); return false;">Bacon Coinber</a></span></p>
